</paragraph>
<paragraph id="03421E604C70FF87FEE9FB796ED7FB51" blockId="22.[264,1323,670,1438]" pageId="22" pageNumber="23">
Evenhuis &amp; Greathead, 
<number id="B5350C474C70FF87FDE8FB796D02FB0E" box="[569,626,1179,1202]" pageId="22" pageNumber="23" value="1999.0">1999</number>
